Detailed Description

template<class BaseReportT = Aeryn::VerboseReport>
class Aeryn::XcodeReport< BaseReportT >

XCodeReport.

The XCode report uses a file based cookie to stop the tests begin run if the code has not been changed. It's templated so that it can take on the behavior of any of the other reports. By default it uses the verbose report. The XCode report is intended for use with the apple mac IDE XCode.

Author:
Thaddaues Froggley and Paul Grenyer
